title: [Nielira Harbor, Naefira Pier]
description: The tall lattice-curved arches frame the ends of the ebony-planked pier, the ivy-draped trellises suspending a vine-framed haon sign between the unfurling onyx roses.  A series of nautical maps sketched in vivid pigments are affixed to a haon board, protected by a panel of clear glass flanked by a duo of open signal fans.  A wrought pewter bench sits beside a stack of hemp-bound crates, the containers branded in a port-encircled cityscape.
